So is this all my fault?

10
00:01:43,970 --> 00:01:45,472
Me. Ben Willis.

11
00:01:48,475 --> 00:01:53,480
It's funny what goes through
your mind at a time like this.

12
00:01:53,515 --> 00:01:56,983
The two-and-a-half years
we spent together.

13
00:01:58,985 --> 00:02:00,987
The promises we made.

14
00:02:04,491 --> 00:02:07,994
The holidays we took
with her parents.

15
00:02:09,496 --> 00:02:12,999
The lamp we bought
