It was my final year
at art college.

17
00:02:22,008 --> 00:02:23,510
And in the weeks that
followed the breakup,

18
00:02:23,545 --> 00:02:26,513
I tried to figure out
what went wrong.

19
00:02:26,548 --> 00:02:28,515
Why did we break up?

20
00:02:29,015 --> 00:02:33,019
It's funny, but when I think back
now the reason seems so small.

21
00:02:33,054 --> 00:02:36,523
One day she's with me,
and she's saying "i love you,"

22
00:02:36,558 --> 00:02:40,026
And the next week
she's with someone else.

23
00:02:40,061 --> 00:02:42,529
Probably saying
the same thing.

24
00:02:42,564 --> 00:02:44,531
So did she
really love me?

25
00:02:45,532 --> 00:02:47,499
What is love anyway?

26
00:02:47,534 --> 00:02:50,537
And is it really
that fleeting?

27
00:02:53,540 --> 00:02:56,007
Forget about her. You
don't wanna waste your time.

28
00:02:56,042 --> 00:03:00,046
Thinking about a girl that dumped
you for a loser like Steve Jenkins.

29
00:03:00,081 --> 00:03:03,014
She didn't dump me

30
00:03:03,049 --> 00:03:05,051
Why did she
chuck you anyway?

31
00:03:06,553 --> 00:03:08,019
It ended

32
00:03:08,054 --> 00:03:11,057
'Cause Suzy thinks the grass is
always greener on the other side.

33
00:03:11,558 --> 00:03:15,061
She's always worrying about there
being a better party to go to.

34
00:03:15,562 --> 00:03:19,030
Or a better boyfriend to be had.

35
00:03:19,065 --> 00:03:21,568
I just felt I could
never make her happy

36
00:03:25,572 --> 00:03:28,575
And then Steve Jenkins
started texting her.

37
00:03:28,610 --> 00:03:31,578
How did Steve Jenkins
get her number?

38
00:03:31,613 --> 00:03:33,545
It was a good point.

39
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:36,082
I only imagined the worst.

40
00:03:37,584 --> 00:03:40,051
I don't want to think about it.

41
00:03:40,086 --> 00:03:42,589
You need to go out with a beautiful
girl. A model or something.

42
00:03:43,089 --> 00:03:44,556
Why?

43
00:03:44,591 --> 00:03:47,093
Well, because if you've got
a beautiful girl on your arm,

44
00:03:47,594 --> 00:03:49,060
Then you must
be worth having.

45
00:03:49,095 --> 00:03:51,062
Women are in competition
with each other, you see.

46
00:03:51,097 --> 00:03:54,100
Suzy sees you with a sexy baby,
she'll think to herself

47
