Ben, Mr. Adams here has
given his time up for you.

55
00:05:04,671 --> 00:05:08,675
Don't you think we should show
him a little bit of respect?

56
00:05:16,683 --> 00:05:19,686
Excuse me.

57
00:05:25,325 --> 00:05:28,828
I live in student accommodation
not far from the college.

58
00:05:29,329 --> 00:05:32,582
It's basically
a four-story concrete block

59
00:05:32,617 --> 00:05:35,835
Housing some 120
hormone-crazed students.

60
00:05:43,343 --> 00:05:45,345
This is the haunting period.

61
00:05:45,845 --> 00:05:49,349
The time when the demons
of regret come for you.

62
00:05:51,351 --> 00:05:53,353
She stood right there

63
00:05:53,853 --> 00:05:56,356
When I said those words:

64
00:05:56,856 --> 00:05:57,822
"I'm sorry.

65
00:05:57,857 --> 00:06:00,860
"I don't think
i can make you happy.

66
00:06:00,895 --> 00:06:02,862
Maybe we should break up."

67
00:06:04,364 --> 00:06:06,366
And that's when
she got angry.

68
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,891
Hello?

69
00:06:34,394 --> 00:06:36,396
Suzy, it's me, Ben.

70
00:06:36,896 --> 00:06:40,400
Ben! I was asleep.
What is it?

71
00:06:41,901 --> 00:06:44,404
Suzy, um...

72
00:06:46,406 --> 00:06:48,658
I'm sorry.

73
00:06:48,693 --> 00:06:50,910
